Title: Ray Liotta has passed away.
Narrative:
Ray Liotta has passed away at the age of 67. The actor was very well known for his role as Henry Hill in the Martin Scorcese classic, "Goodfellas." 

The actor died in his sleep, he was shooting for a movie "Dangerous Waters" in the Dominican Republic.

May he rest in peace.
